<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>GigHive - Connecting Talent with Opportunity</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.3.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body, html {
            height: 100%;
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #FFF8E7; /* Light Honey Yellow */
        }

        .hero-section {
            background-image: url('https://via.placeholder.com/1920x800/FFD700/000000?text=GigHive+Landing+Page'); /* Replace with your actual image URL */
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            color: #000; /* Black text for contrast */
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10% 0;
        }

        .hero-section h1 {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); /* White text shadow */
        }

        .hero-section p {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); /* White text shadow */
        }

        .btn-primary-custom {
            background-color: #FFD700; /* Hive Yellow */
            border-color: #FFD700;
            color: #212529; /* Dark text for contrast */
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 0.7rem 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            transition: transform 0.2s ease-in-out, box-shadow 0.2s ease-in-out, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out;
        }

        .btn-primary-custom:hover {
            background-color: #FFA500; /* Sunset Orange */
            border-color: #FFA500;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0px 6px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-secondary-custom {
            background-color: #fff; /* White */
            border-color: #fff;
            color: #212529; /* Dark text for contrast */
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 0.7rem 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            transition: transform 0.2s ease-in-out, box-shadow 0.2s ease-in-out, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out;
        }

        .btn-secondary-custom:hover {
            background-color: #f0f0f0; /* Light Grey */
            border-color: #f0f0f0;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0px 6px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .features-section {
            background-color: #FFF8E7; /* Light Honey Yellow */
            padding: 4rem 0;
        }

        .features-section h2 {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #333; /* Dark text for readability */
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .features-section .card {
            background-color: #fff; /* White background for cards */
            border: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); /* Subtle shadow */
            transition: transform 0.2s ease-in-out, box-shadow 0.2s ease-in-out;
        }

        .features-section .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0px 6px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .features-section .card-body {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .features-section .card-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #333;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        .features-section .card-text {
            color: #555; /* Slightly darker text */
        }

        .features-section .fa-3x {
            color: #FFD700; /* Hive Yellow for icons */
        }

        .how-it-works-section {
            padding: 4rem 0;
            background-color: #faf5e6;
        }

        .how-it-works-section h2 {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #333; /* Dark text for readability */
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .how-it-works-section .step {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .how-it-works-section .step i {
            color: #FFD700; /* Hive Yellow for icons */
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .how-it-works-section .step h4 {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #333;
        }

        .how-it-works-section .step p {
            color: #555; /* Slightly darker text */
        }

        .call-to-action-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFD700, #FFA500); /* Gradient background */
            color: #212529; /* Dark text for contrast */
            text-align: center;
            padding: 4rem 0;
        }

        .call-to-action-section h2 {
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .call-to-action-section p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .call-to-action-section .btn-dark {
            background-color: #343a40; /* Dark button for contrast */
            border-color: #343a40;
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 0.7rem 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            transition: transform 0.2s ease-in-out, box-shadow 0.2s ease-in-out, background-color 0.2s ease-in-out;
        }

        .call-to-action-section .btn-dark:hover {
            background-color: #23272b; /* Slightly darker shade on hover */
            border-color: #23272b;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0px 6px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }
         .footer {
            background-color: #212529;
            color: #FFF;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1rem 0;
            position: relative; /* Ensure it stays at the bottom */
            width: 100%;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #FFD700; /* Hive Yellow */
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        .footer a:hover {
            color: #FFA500; /* Sunset Orange */
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <section class="hero-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to GigHive</h1>
            <p class="lead">Connecting Talent with Opportunity</p>
            <a href="<%= new_user_registration_path %>" class="btn btn-primary-custom btn-lg shadow">Join Now</a>
            <a href="<%= new_user_session_path %>" class="btn btn-secondary-custom btn-lg shadow">Sign In</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="features-section" id="features">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="text-center">Our Features</h2>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card mb-4 shadow-sm">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <i class="fas fa-search fa-3x"></i>
                            <h5 class="card-title mt-3">Browse Freelancers</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Find talented professionals across various fields to execute your projects.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card mb-4 shadow-sm">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <i class="fas fa-clipboard-list fa-3x"></i>
                            <h5 class="card-title mt-3">Post Projects</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Describe your project needs and receive proposals from qualified freelancers.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card mb-4 shadow-sm">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <i class="fas fa-shield-alt fa-3x"></i>
                            <h5 class="card-title mt-3">Secure Payments</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Manage transactions safely with our integrated payment system.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="how-it-works-section" id="how-it-works">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="text-center">How It Works</h2>
            <div class="row text-center">
                <div class="col-md-3 step">
                    <i class="fas fa-user-plus fa-4x"></i>
                    <h4>Sign Up</h4>
                    <p>Create an account to get started.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3 step">
                    <i class="fas fa-tasks fa-4x"></i>
                    <h4>Post or Find a Task</h4>
                    <p>Detail your project requirements or find tasks that match your skills.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3 step">
                    <i class="fas fa-comments fa-4x"></i>
                    <h4>Collaborate</h4>
                    <p>Communicate with freelancers or clients to refine the project.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3 step">
                    <i class="fas fa-money-check-alt fa-4x"></i>
                    <h4>Complete & Pay</h4>
                    <p>Finalize the project and process payments securely.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="call-to-action-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Join the GigHive Community Today!</h2>
            <p>Whether you're looking to hire top talent or offer your expert skills, GigHive is the perfect platform for you.</p>
            <a href="<%= new_user_registration_path %>" class="btn btn-dark btn-lg shadow">Get Started</a>
        </div>
    </section>
    <div class="footer">
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; <%= Time.current.year %> GigHive. All rights reserved. | <a href="<%= pages_terms_path %>">Terms of Service</a> | <a href="<%= pages_privacy_path %>">Privacy Policy</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.1/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>